




{"id":16176,"date":"2025-03-24T09:43:32","date_gmt":"2025-03-24T02:43:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=16176"},"modified":"2025-04-02T11:57:34","modified_gmt":"2025-04-02T04:57:34","slug":"inno-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-nhan-hieu-innosmart-buoc-tien-moi-trong-cong-nghe-giao-duc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/inno-viet-nam-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-nhan-hieu-innosmart-buoc-tien-moi-trong-cong-nghe-giao-duc\/","title":{"rendered":"INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u INNOSMART \u2013 B\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn m\u1edbi trong c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p data-start=\"152\" data-end=\"423\">INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u INNOSMART &#8211; D\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u00f4ng minh d\u00e0nh cho Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"670\">T\u1eeb nay, <strong>t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd mang nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u INNOSMART<\/strong>, cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng minh to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"670\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16219\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Ra-mat-INNOSMART-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"675\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Ra-mat-INNOSMART-1.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Ra-mat-INNOSMART-1-533x400.webp 533w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Ra-mat-INNOSMART-1-768x576.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/Ra-mat-INNOSMART-1-600x450.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"543\" data-end=\"608\"><strong data-start=\"547\" data-end=\"606\">INNOSMART \u2013 Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"610\" data-end=\"964\">V\u1edbi s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh &#8220;\u0110\u1ed5i m\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc&#8221;, INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho ng\u00e0nh gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c. T\u1eeb nay, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd mang th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u INNOSMART, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 cam k\u1ebft mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"966\" data-end=\"1132\">INNOSMART kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u00ean g\u1ecdi m\u1edbi m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n cao h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 v\u00e0 t\u00ednh \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c.<\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"1134\" data-end=\"1187\"><strong data-start=\"1138\" data-end=\"1185\">C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m thu\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u INNOSMART<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"1189\" data-end=\"1295\">D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u INNOSMART, INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd cung c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, bao g\u1ed3m:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"257\" data-end=\"288\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c<\/strong> \u2013 Bao g\u1ed3m m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb gi\u00fap t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ednh tr\u1ef1c quan trong gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"397\" data-end=\"431\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong> \u2013 Bao g\u1ed3m h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, t\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a,&#8230; H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc, gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"530\" data-end=\"563\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn<\/strong> \u2013 Bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb xa, gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"677\" data-end=\"700\">N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong> \u2013 B\u00e0n gh\u1ebf c\u00f4ng th\u00e1i h\u1ecdc, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u00e0 linh ho\u1ea1t gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"801\" data-end=\"822\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m Inclass+<\/strong> \u2013 H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc th\u00f4ng minh, gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng theo d\u00f5i v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 h\u1ecdc sinh trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"942\" data-end=\"961\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb s\u1ed1 h\u00f3a<\/strong> \u2013 C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m gi\u00fap chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u gi\u1ea5y th\u00e0nh d\u1eef li\u1ec7u s\u1ed1, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u01b0u tr\u1eef th\u00f4ng tin hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"1070\" data-end=\"1102\">Thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong> \u2013 H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an ninh, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tra c\u1ee9u, m\u01b0\u1ee3n\/tr\u1ea3 s\u00e1ch t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"1185\" data-end=\"1207\">T\u1ee7 s\u00e1ch th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong> \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p l\u01b0u tr\u1eef v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u kh\u00f4ng gian th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"1295\" data-end=\"1327\">Ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong> \u2013 \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean th\u01b0 vi\u1ec7n, k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n d\u1eef li\u1ec7u \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"255\" data-end=\"1542\"><strong data-start=\"1424\" data-end=\"1444\">Robot th\u00f4ng minh<\/strong> \u2013 H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh, gi\u00fap h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"1544\" data-end=\"1776\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\">V\u1edbi d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m INNOSMART, INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng minh, gi\u00fap n\u00e2ng cao hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho h\u1ecdc sinh<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"1544\" data-end=\"1776\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16213\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/banner-web-INNOSMART-1.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"1920\" height=\"810\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/banner-web-INNOSMART-1.webp 1920w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/banner-web-INNOSMART-1-800x338.webp 800w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/banner-web-INNOSMART-1-1400x591.webp 1400w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/banner-web-INNOSMART-1-768x324.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/banner-web-INNOSMART-1-1536x648.webp 1536w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/banner-web-INNOSMART-1-600x253.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3 data-start=\"2033\" data-end=\"2098\"><strong data-start=\"2037\" data-end=\"2096\">T\u1ea1i sao INNOSMART l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u cho gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2687\"><strong data-start=\"2674\" data-end=\"2692\">K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i s\u1ed1 h\u00f3a<\/strong> \u2013 Gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u1edbi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2687\"><strong data-start=\"2772\" data-end=\"2796\">T\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y<\/strong> \u2013 H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1t ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2687\"><strong data-start=\"2856\" data-end=\"2884\">M\u1edf r\u1ed9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp<\/strong> \u2013 H\u1ecdc sinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c tr\u1ef1c quan, sinh \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2100\" data-end=\"2687\"><strong data-start=\"2949\" data-end=\"2983\">Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng h\u01a1n<\/strong> \u2013 C\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 data-start=\"2689\" data-end=\"2758\"><strong data-start=\"2693\" data-end=\"2756\">INNOSMART \u2013 H\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p data-start=\"2760\" data-end=\"3071\">INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p m\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng minh. V\u1edbi INNOSMART, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc trong vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1, gi\u00fap gi\u00e1o vi\u00ean gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u01a1n v\u00e0 h\u1ecdc sinh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ecdc t\u1eadp t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p data-start=\"3073\" data-end=\"3154\"><strong>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 h\u1ec7 sinh th\u00e1i INNOSMART \u2013 Gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c th\u00f4ng minh to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n!<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>INNO Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u INNOSMART &#8211; D\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m th\u00f4ng minh d\u00e0nh cho Gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd nh\u1eb1m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m gi\u1ea3ng d\u1ea1y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ea1i m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng gi\u00e1o d\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. T\u1eeb nay, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":16219,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-16176","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16176","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=16176"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16176\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":16221,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/16176\/revisions\/16221"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16219"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=16176"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=16176"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=16176"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}